[normal]1.7
[normal] 
[normal]We believe that the public want healthy 
[normal]food that is good value for money, the production of which does not damage the natural environment
[normal].
[normal] Against this background, 
[normal]it is hard to argue against the value of 
[normal]spending taxpayers
[normal]’
[normal] money on programmes w
[normal]hose outcomes will benefit 
[normal]nature
[normal], 
[normal]the long term 
[normal]viability of farming
